  "remarks": "JSC Krymtelecom is a telecommunications company that provides telecommunications services in Crimea. JSC Krymtelecom has obtained licences from the Russian authorities to provide various telecommunications servicesin Russia and in illegally annexed Crimea and Sevastopol. JSC Krymtelecom receives substantial financial support from the Russian Federation to continue its business operations.",
